From: Bernhard Reutner-Fischer <rep.dot.nop@gmail.com>
Date: Thu, 9 Apr 2015 14:43:30 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] AC_PROG_MKDIR_P: Also accept BusyBox mkdir -p

* lib/autoconf/programs.m4 (AC_PROG_MKDIR_P): Accept BusyBox.

Signed-off-by: Bernhard Reutner-Fischer <rep.dot.nop@gmail.com>
---
 lib/autoconf/programs.m4 | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/lib/autoconf/programs.m4 b/lib/autoconf/programs.m4
index 59df1a2..8ebcf9e 100644
--- a/lib/autoconf/programs.m4
+++ b/lib/autoconf/programs.m4
@@ -672,6 +672,7 @@ if test -z "$MKDIR_P"; then
 	   AS_EXECUTABLE_P(["$as_dir$ac_prog$ac_exec_ext"]) || continue
 	   case `"$as_dir$ac_prog$ac_exec_ext" --version 2>&1` in #(
 	     'mkdir (GNU coreutils) '* | \
+	     'BusyBox '* | \
 	     'mkdir (coreutils) '* | \
 	     'mkdir (fileutils) '4.1*)
 	       ac_cv_path_mkdir=$as_dir$ac_prog$ac_exec_ext
